annotationA: 60S ribosomal protein L27a; Structural constituent of ribosome. It is involved in the biological process described with: mitotic spindle elongation; translation; centrosome duplication; mitotic spindle organization; Belongs to the universal ribosomal protein uL15 family
annotationB: LD28793p; GTPase activity; translation elongation factor activity; GTP binding.
